Paper: hep-th/9806077

Date: 1998-06-10

Title: Deconstructing Supersymmetry

Authors: N.S.Manton

Comments: 19 pages, Tex file

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 40 (1999) 736-750

Two supersymmetric classical mechanical systems are discussed. Concreterealizations are obtained by supposing that the dynamical variables take valuesin a Grassmann algebra with two generators. The equations of motion areexplicitly solved.